    The 64K limit on paragraphs has been removed in Notes/Domino 6. To ensure backward compatibility, "large" paragraphs are broken into smaller paragraphs which are bracketed by a CDLARGEPARAGRAPH record with its Flags member set to CDLARGEPARAGRAPH_BEGIN and a CDLARGEPARAGRAPH record with its Flags member set to CDLARGEPARAGRAPH_END.
